creator: LittleLives
descriptionHtml:
Attention all Preschool educators, ever lost track of what time your students were dropped off by their parents? Well, LittleLives’ new Check-in app is here to help!

LittleLives, ranked Number 1 by AECES (Association for Early Childhood Educators (Singapore)) and used by over 300 preschools has just added a cool new Check-in App.

Students reporting for school can easily snap a photo with their parents, upload, and the time automatically recorded. It’s that easy!

Keeping track of your students’ movements will now be a breeze.

So hurry teachers, download this cool new app that makes coming to school fun for students!

Key features for the check-in app:
+ Photo-taking of the students with their parents.
+ Automatically takes attendance.
+ Automatically records the time the students arrives and leaves school with their caregiver.
descriptionShort: Download this cool new app that makes coming to school fun for students!

Attention all Preschool educators, ever lost track of what time your students were dropped off by their parents? Well, LittleLives’ new Check-in app is here to help!

LittleLives, ranked Number 1 by AECES (Association for Early Childhood Educators (Singapore)) and used by over 300 preschools has just added a cool new Check-in App.

Students reporting for school can easily snap a photo with their parents, upload, and the time automatically recorded. It’s that easy!

Keeping track of your students’ movements will now be a breeze.

So hurry teachers, download this cool new app that makes coming to school fun for students!

Key features for the check-in app:
+ Photo-taking of the students with their parents.
+ Automatically takes attendance.
+ Automatically records the time the students arrives and leaves school with their caregiver.
descriptionShort: Download this cool new app that makes coming to school fun for students!
